### Phase 2: Backend API (FastAPI)

---

#### [MODIFY] [goals.py](file:///Users/aditya4/Desktop/Budget-Bandhu/budget-bandhu-rag/api/routes/goals.py)

Add on-chain awareness to existing goal routes:
- `POST /api/v1/goals/{user_id}` — now also stores `contract_goal_id`, `tx_hash`, `goal_type: "personal" | "escrow"`
- `POST /api/v1/goals/{goal_id}/progress` — **new** — accepts CSV upload or manual salary input, runs ML savings calculation, updates MongoDB + calls smart contract `updateProgress`
- `GET /api/v1/goals/{goal_id}/chain-status` — reads on-chain goal state

---

#### [NEW] [escrow.py](file:///Users/aditya4/Desktop/Budget-Bandhu/budget-bandhu-rag/api/routes/escrow.py)

New route file for group escrow pools:
- `POST /api/v1/escrow/create` — stores pool in MongoDB, returns `poolId` for invite link
- `GET /api/v1/escrow/{pool_id}` — pool details + member list + contribution status
- `POST /api/v1/escrow/{pool_id}/progress` — calculates group savings progress via ML
- `GET /api/v1/escrow/invite/{pool_id}` — generates shareable invite link data

