| **1a** | Write + test `PersonalGoalSBT.sol` | ~2 hours |
| **1b** | Write + test `EscrowPool.sol` | ~3 hours |
| **1c** | Deploy both to Amoy, save addresses | ~30 min |
| **2a** | Backend: modify goals.py + add escrow.py | ~2 hours |
| **2b** | Backend: ML savings calculation endpoint | ~1 hour |
| **3a** | Frontend: contract hooks + ABIs | ~1 hour |
| **3b** | Frontend: rebuild goals page (3 tabs) | ~3 hours |
| **3c** | Frontend: escrow invite/join flow | ~2 hours |
| **3d** | Frontend: SBT badge display + gamification | ~1 hour |

**Total: ~15-16 hours of work across ~4-5 sessions**

