## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Hardhat unit tests for both contracts: `npx hardhat test` — test goal creation, progress update, completion, SBT minting, escrow contribute/complete/refund, edge cases (double-complete, early withdrawal)
- This is the MOST critical verification since contracts are immutable once deployed

### Manual Verification
1. **Contract deployment**: Deploy to Amoy → verify on [amoy.polygonscan.com](https://amoy.polygonscan.com) → call `Read Contract` to confirm initial state
2. **Personal goal flow**: Create goal via frontend → MetaMask popup → confirm on Polygonscan → upload CSV → see progress update → complete → see SBT in wallet
3. **Escrow flow**: Create pool → share invite link → open in incognito with different MetaMask account → join → both contribute → complete → both receive SBTs
4. **Edge case**: Let deadline expire on an incomplete escrow pool → verify refund works

> [!IMPORTANT]
> You will need **testnet POL** in at least 2 MetaMask accounts to test the escrow flow. Get from [faucet.polygon.technology](https://faucet.polygon.technology).
